                    "id": "secondary-content",
                    "title": "How we use your data",
                    "content": [{
                        "list": ["You cannot appeal your selection. Your business was selected to give us a comprehensive view of the UK economy.", "The information you provide contributes to Gross Domestic Product (GDP)."]
